Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.95,0:00:07.23,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I hope Shining Armor and princess Cadence don't think
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.23,0:00:10.33,Twilight,,0,0,0,,it's too soon for me to come back to the Crystal Empirefor for a visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.33,0:00:12.82,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But I just know Flurry Heart's grown so much already.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:15.14,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I'll even recognize her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.14,0:00:17.43,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,She is the only baby they have, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.43,0:00:20.86,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I think it will be pretty easy to figure out who she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.05,0:00:25.32,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I know you want to visit your niece as much as possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.32,0:00:27.62,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,and I'm excited to see Sunburst again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.62,0:00:31.22,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I just don't wanna fall behind on my friendship lessons back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.22,0:00:34.68,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Starlight, your work in Ponyville isn't going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.68,0:00:38.37,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Besides, I think we all know you can learn about friendship anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.37,0:00:40.59,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Right, Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.59,0:00:43.64,Spike,,0,0,0,,"Spike?" Who's "Spike"?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.49,0:00:46.96,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Pfft. Uh, you're Spike, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.96,0:00:49.24,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,And why are you dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.69,0:00:51.95,Spike,,0,0,0,,Guys, you're blowing my cover!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.44,0:00:54.05,Spike,,0,0,0,,How'd you even know it was me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.05,0:00:56.69,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Because you're you…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.69,0:00:58.66,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,in a coat, hat and glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.66,0:01:00.66,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Also, we're the only ones here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.50,0:01:02.96,Spike,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.96,0:01:05.75,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Spike, why do you need a disguise?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.75,0:01:07.67,Spike,,0,0,0,,Last time we came to the Crystal Empire,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.67,0:01:10.34,Spike,,0,0,0,,there was a lot goin' on with the new baby and the Crystalling,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.34,0:01:12.97,Spike,,0,0,0,,but I still got mobbed in the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.97,0:01:15.64,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't say mobbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.64,0:01:17.83,Spike,,0,0,0,,And this is just a family visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.83,0:01:20.29,Spike,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't want the presence of Spike the Brave and Glorious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.29,0:01:23.16,Spike,,0,0,0,,to turn it into some kind of circus.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.16,0:01:23.94,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,We get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.94,0:01:25.88,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,The Crystal Ponies adore you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.88,0:01:27.59,Twilight,,0,0,0,,He did save the Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.59,0:01:28.98,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.98,0:01:33.34,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But still, I don't think your presence will turn our visit into a circus.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.34,0:01:36.24,Spike,,0,0,0,,Not if I find the right disguise, it won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.81,0:02:22.71,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Disguise or not, Spike,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.71,0:02:25.73,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I don't think you need to worry about being mobbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.73,0:02:28.10,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Nopony's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.25,0:02:31.07,Spike,,0,0,0,,It's like a ghost town.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.07,0:02:33.89,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I've got a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.55,0:02:42.98,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this is weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.98,0:02:45.41,Spike,,0,0,0,,I guess I don't need the disguise after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.04,0:02:50.53,SomeponyYellow,,0,0,0,,It's Spike the Brave and Glorious!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.53,0:02:53.37,SomeponyBluishWhite,,0,0,0,,He's come to save us yet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.37,0:02:55.99,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Spike! Spike! Spike! Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.99,0:02:57.80,Spike,,0,0,0,,Save you from what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.80,0:02:59.47,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.47,0:03:01.97,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Why was everypony hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.97,0:03:05.58,SomeponyLightPink,,0,0,0,,Oh, it sure looks like Princess Twilight and her pupil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:07.71,SomeponyYellow,,0,0,0,,But how can we be sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.71,0:03:12.06,SomeponyOrange,,0,0,0,,We can't! Either one of them could be the… you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.10,0:03:16.30,SomeponyLightPink,,0,0,0,,What if this…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:17.39,SomeponyLightPink,,0,0,0,,isn't…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.39,0:03:19.72,SomeponyLightPink,,0,0,0,,the real Spike?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:22.74,SomeponyYellow,,0,0,0,,Everypony run!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:25.86,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.86,0:03:28.74,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Something strange is definitely going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:31.13,Spike,,0,0,0,,Ya think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:36.06,Guard,,0,0,0,,Who goes there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.06,0:03:39.96,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Um, you don't recognize the Princess of Friendship?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.96,0:03:41.81,Guard,,0,0,0,,Of course we recognize her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.81,0:03:43.81,Guard2,,0,0,0,,But that doesn't mean it's really her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.69,0:03:47.40,Spike,,0,0,0,,It's okay, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.40,0:03:48.56,Spike,,0,0,0,,They're with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.56,0:03:50.57,Spike,,0,0,0,,And any friend of Spike the Brave and Glorious
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.57,0:03:53.85,Spike,,0,0,0,,is a friend of the Crystal Empire, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.16,0:03:58.41,Guard2,,0,0,0,,It does look like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.41,0:04:00.22,Guard,,0,0,0,,Well, it would, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.22,0:04:03.53,Guard,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but we'll need to see some proof of identification.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.53,0:04:05.53,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,We'll take care of things from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.17,0:04:09.63,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, Cadance, thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.63,0:04:11.48,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:13.48,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,We can explain, Twily…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:15.48,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,if it really is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:20.11,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,Sunshine, sunshine…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:21.54,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,…ladybugs awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:21.54,Twilight,,0,0,0,,…ladybugs awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.54,0:04:24.60,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,Clap your hooves and do a little shake!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.54,0:04:24.60,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Clap your hooves and do a little shake!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.25,0:04:28.15,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,It's okay, everypony!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.15,0:04:29.38,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,It's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:34.34,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Of course, it's her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.34,0:04:35.68,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,What's this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.68,0:04:38.05,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,A changeling's been spotted nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.05,0:04:39.27,Twilight,,0,0,0,,A changeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.27,0:04:40.32,Spike,,0,0,0,,That's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.32,0:04:41.98,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.98,0:04:44.19,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,After Queen Chrysalis took my place at our wedding
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.19,0:04:46.82,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,and invaded Canterlot with her army of minions,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:49.35,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,we're not taking any chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:51.15,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Changelings feed off love.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.15,0:04:52.85,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,And ever since Flurry Heart's Crystalling,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:56.55,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,the Empire is filled with more love than anywhere in Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.55,0:04:59.12,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,It's possible they've come for the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.12,0:05:02.14,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,That's why we posted the extra guards, and why we're…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.14,0:05:04.28,Twilight,,0,0,0,,…checking everypony's identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:06.49,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:09.73,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,Flurry Heart's really been looking forward to seeing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:14.49,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, she's gotten so big.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.49,0:05:18.23,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Starlight and I will do whatever we can to help protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.23,0:05:22.44,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,To be honest, having you here is already a big relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.79,0:05:29.30,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,The royal guards were wondering if Spike the Brave and Glorious
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:32.01,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,would like to join in the search for the changeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.01,0:05:33.39,Spike,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:36.16,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I don't know if that's such a good idea, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.16,0:05:37.87,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It sounds dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:41.97,Spike,,0,0,0,,Come on, Twilight, this is Spike the Brave and Glorious you're talking to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.97,0:05:44.69,Spike,,0,0,0,,Have you ever known me to run from danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:48.17,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,He'll be safe with our guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.17,0:05:52.30,Spike,,0,0,0,,Or will your guards be safe with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.86,0:05:59.48,Guard2,,0,0,0,,Spike the Brave and Glorious, you've faced the evil changelings before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.48,0:06:00.57,Guard2,,0,0,0,,What can you tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.79,0:06:06.15,Spike,,0,0,0,,Well, they are changelings, so they can… change.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.15,0:06:07.13,Guard2,,0,0,0,,You hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:10.59,Guard2,,0,0,0,,These monsters can look like any of us, so be on guard, guards!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:12.59,Guard2,,0,0,0,,Even more than normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.59,0:06:15.35,Spike,,0,0,0,,And they could be anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.87,0:06:19.17,Spike,,0,0,0,,So we should cover as much ground as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:22.41,Spike,,0,0,0,,You, search that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.41,0:06:24.43,Spike,,0,0,0,,And, you, search that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:29.82,Spike,,0,0,0,,And… I'll…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:32.22,Spike,,0,0,0,,just search… here, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:34.58,Spike,,0,0,0,,Not many places to hide…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.36,0:06:37.95,Spike,,0,0,0,,Unless that rock is a changeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.95,0:06:39.66,Spike,,0,0,0,,Okay, rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.66,0:06:41.66,Spike,,0,0,0,,How do I know you're really a rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:45.11,Spike,,0,0,0,,Not talkin', huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.11,0:06:46.90,Spike,,0,0,0,,Well, you can't fool me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.27,0:06:48.19,Spike,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:51.16,Spike,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.63,0:06:54.77,Spike,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.89,0:07:03.95,Spike,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.95,0:07:07.79,Spike,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's time Spike the Brave and Glorious went back to…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.79,0:07:09.65,Spike,,0,0,0,,protect those guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:13.27,Spike,,0,0,0,,Just my reflection.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.23,0:07:25.38,Spike,,0,0,0,,Just my imagination, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.59,0:07:37.58,Spike,,0,0,0,,Ch-ch-ch-ch-ch-ch-Changeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.67,0:07:41.19,Thorax,,0,0,0,,No, wait! Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.51,0:07:50.60,Spike,,0,0,0,,This is unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.01,0:07:55.01,Thorax,,0,0,0,,The ice is pretty slippery.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.01,0:07:58.03,Thorax,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't want you to get hurt because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:01.50,Spike,,0,0,0,,You… saved me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:02.77,Thorax,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:05.89,Thorax,,0,0,0,,I know you don't wanna be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.97,0:08:08.85,Spike,Spike,0,0,0,,Wait! I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:11.96,Spike,Spike,0,0,0,,Changelings are supposed to be evil… right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.41,0:08:13.03,Thorax,Thorax,0,0,0,,Evil?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.15,0:08:14.49,Thorax,Thorax,0,0,0,,Oh, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.65,0:08:16.57,Thorax,Thorax,0,0,0,,All I've ever wanted is a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.15,0:08:20.97,Thorax,Thorax,0,0,0,,From the moment I first split my egg in the nursery hive…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.37,0:08:36.55,Thorax,Thorax,0,0,0,,I was part of the attack on Canterlot during the Royal Wedding,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.69,0:08:39.07,Thorax,Thorax,0,0,0,,but I'd never seen true friendship like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.07,0:08:41.73,Thorax,Thorax,0,0,0,,And I couldn't just steal it and feed on its love,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.17,0:08:43.73,Thorax,Thorax,0,0,0,,I wanted to share it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.05,0:08:49.29,Thorax,Thorax,0,0,0,,After that, I knew I couldn't live with my kind any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.85,0:08:52.37,Thorax,Thorax,0,0,0,,I set off looking for love to share, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.93,0:08:54.15,Spike,Spike,0,0,0,,But… what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.41,0:08:55.81,Thorax,Thorax,0,0,0,,I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.19,0:08:59.53,Thorax,Thorax,0,0,0,,And there's so much love in the Crystal Empire right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.53,0:09:01.21,Thorax,Thorax,0,0,0,,it's what drew me here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.21,0:09:03.85,Thorax,Thorax,0,0,0,,It's driving me crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.05,0:09:05.93,Spike,Spike,0,0,0,,That would be from the royal Crystalling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.95,0:09:09.01,Spike,Spike,0,0,0,,It's pretty much a giant outpouring of love for the new baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.35,0:09:12.43,Thorax,Thorax,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.67,0:09:14.09,Thorax,Thorax,0,0,0,,I'm just so hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.25,0:09:18.07,Thorax,Thorax,0,0,0,,If I had a friend, maybe the love we shared could sustain me, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.25,0:09:20.89,Thorax,Thorax,0,0,0,,I don't think the crystal ponies wanna be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.15,0:09:27.01,Spike,Spike,0,0,0,,What if I told you there was somepony they respect and admire so much
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.15,0:09:29.19,Spike,Spike,0,0,0,,that could convince them to give it a try?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:31.07,Thorax,Thorax,0,0,0,,If only that were true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.19,0:09:33.75,Spike,Spike,0,0,0,,It is! I mean, I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.01,0:09:35.51,Spike,Spike,0,0,0,,It's me, Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.15,0:09:40.13,Spike,Spike,0,0,0,,Spike the Brave and Glorious?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.31,0:09:41.89,Spike,Spike,0,0,0,,I'm sure you've heard of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.49,0:09:44.91,Thorax,Thorax,0,0,0,,Nope. But I was raised by an evil queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.03,0:09:46.23,Thorax,Thorax,0,0,0,,I'm Thorax.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.33,0:09:48.57,Thorax,Thorax,0,0,0,,I can't believe you want to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.05,0:09:49.63,Spike,Spike,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.97,0:09:52.47,Spike,Spike,0,0,0,,Hasn't anypony ever just been nice to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.25,0:09:57.37,Thorax,Thorax,0,0,0,,S-Sorry, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.67,0:10:00.07,Thorax,Thorax,0,0,0,,Kindness like that kind of brings it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.47,0:10:02.25,Thorax,Thorax,0,0,0,,You still wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:03.85,Spike,Spike,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:06.15,Spike,Spike,0,0,0,,And I am one hundred percent sure
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.15,0:10:08.75,Spike,Spike,0,0,0,,I can get the whole Crystal Empire to be your friend too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.51,0:10:13.75,Spike,Spike,0,0,0,,But… maybe I should just…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.95,0:10:15.17,Spike,Spike,0,0,0,,talk to them first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.31,0:10:18.13,Guard,Royal guard 1,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.23,0:10:19.57,Guard,Royal guard 1,0,0,0,,Did you see the Changeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.81,0:10:21.45,Guard2,Royal guard 2,0,0,0,,Did you defeat the evil creature?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.65,0:10:24.13,Spike,Spike,0,0,0,,Defeating a Changeling would be great,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:26.39,Spike,Spike,0,0,0,,but do you know what would be glorious?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.47,0:10:28.39,Guard,Royal guard 1,0,0,0,,Defeating two Changelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.41,0:10:30.67,Guard2,Royal guard 2,0,0,0,,Defeating all the Changelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.29,0:10:33.43,Spike,Spike,0,0,0,,Not having to fight the Changeling at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.45,0:10:35.47,Spike,Spike,0,0,0,,Because I made friends with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.23,0:10:41.89,Guard,Royal guard 1,0,0,0,,For a second I thought you were serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.77,0:10:45.03,Guard2,Royal guard 2,0,0,0,,Could you imagine?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.03,0:10:47.17,Guard2,Royal guard 2,0,0,0,,Friends with a Changeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:48.71,Spike,Spike,0,0,0,,I am serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.71,0:10:50.27,Spike,Spike,0,0,0,,He wants to be friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.17,0:10:56.77,Guard,Royal guard 1,0,0,0,,Not only are you Spike the Brave and Glorious,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.77,0:10:59.03,Guard,Royal guard 1,0,0,0,,you're also Spike the Hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.83,0:11:01.43,Spike,Spike,0,0,0,,I'm not joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:03.03,Spike,Spike,0,0,0,,The changeling is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.83,0:11:09.57,ShiningArmor,Shining Armor,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I don't think it's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.63,0:11:14.11,ShiningArmor,Shining Armor,0,0,0,,The Changeling Queen Chrysalis kidnapped Cadance, and cast a spell on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.01,0:11:20.79,ShiningArmor,Shining Armor,0,0,0,,There's no such thing as a 'nice' Changeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.07,0:11:23.01,Spike,Spike,0,0,0,,…You're right, Shining Armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.01,0:11:23.99,Spike,Spike,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:26.49,Spike,Spike,0,0,0,,That was a… bad joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:30.81,Thorax,Thorax,0,0,0,,So? So? Uh, what did they say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.81,0:11:32.19,Thorax,Thorax,0,0,0,,How many new friends do I have?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:36.37,Spike,Spike,0,0,0,,Well, it didn't go exactly the way I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.47,0:11:41.51,Thorax,Thorax,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:43.29,Thorax,Thorax,0,0,0,,Well, thanks for trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.85,0:11:45.67,Thorax,Thorax,0,0,0,,I guess it's not surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.99,0:11:48.65,Thorax,Thorax,0,0,0,,How can you expect ponies who looks like this…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.53,0:11:53.03,Thorax,Thorax,0,0,0,,to trust something that looks like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.13,0:11:56.99,Spike,Spike,0,0,0,,I think I might know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.38,0:12:07.34,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Spike, if you're done searching for the changeling,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.34,0:12:09.04,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Starlight and I could use your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:11.56,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We're working on a protection spell for Flurry Heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.56,0:12:13.94,Twilight,,0,0,0,,and nopony takes notes like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.82,0:12:20.57,Spike,,0,0,0,,Actually, Twilight, I wanted to introduce you to my friend…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.57,0:12:22.52,Spike,,0,0,0,,Crystal…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.52,0:12:23.63,Spike,,0,0,0,,hoof!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.63,0:12:25.23,Spike,,0,0,0,,Crystalhoof!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.23,0:12:27.48,Spike,,0,0,0,,My good friend, Crystalhoof.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.48,0:12:29.45,Thorax,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.45,0:12:32.62,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Well, it's… nice to meet you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.62,0:12:34.13,Twilight,,0,0,0,,How do you know Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.13,0:12:36.91,Thorax,,0,0,0,,Spike and I go way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.91,0:12:38.29,Spike,,0,0,0,,To the Equestria Games!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:39.57,Spike,,0,0,0,,That's when we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:41.98,Spike,,0,0,0,,We've been pen pals ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.98,0:12:43.67,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Pen pals? Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.67,0:12:46.03,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You could have been using my pen pal quill set!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.03,0:12:47.82,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.82,0:12:49.05,Spike,,0,0,0,,Well, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.05,0:12:53.07,Spike,,0,0,0,,I pretty much only write to him when you and Starlight are studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.07,0:12:58.73,Thorax,,0,0,0,,I like to brag to all my friends about my letters from Spike the Brave and Glorious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.73,0:13:02.25,Spike,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.25,0:13:06.37,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sure Starlight and I can manage, if you want to spend time with your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.37,0:13:09.58,Spike,,0,0,0,,Great! Crystalhoof promised to take me around the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.42,0:13:12.99,Thorax,,0,0,0,,Oh, that was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.99,0:13:14.75,Spike,,0,0,0,,I told ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:48.09,Guard,,0,0,0,,Crystalhoof is nearly as entertaining as Spike himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.61,0:13:54.26,Thorax,,0,0,0,,This place is everything I've ever dreamed of!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.26,0:13:59.25,Thorax,,0,0,0,,But I can't keep pretending to be a crystal pony forever, can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.25,0:14:02.18,Spike,,0,0,0,,Relax, you're winning them over!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.18,0:14:06.03,Spike,,0,0,0,,Pretty soon, nopony will care that you're a changeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:07.32,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.78,0:14:12.75,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,Twilight told me you were off with a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.38,0:14:18.91,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,And any friend of Spike the Brave and Glorious is a friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:27.20,Thorax,,0,0,0,,Oh, she's so beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.20,0:14:30.79,Thorax,,0,0,0,,There's so much love around her…!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.79,0:14:33.20,Thorax,,0,0,0,,I… I…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:37.75,Thorax,,0,0,0,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.75,0:14:40.74,Thorax,,0,0,0,,I'm so… sorry…!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.76,0:14:43.74,Thorax,,0,0,0,,I can't… Can't… stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.74,0:14:46.35,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Spike! Get away from the changeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.35,0:14:49.82,Spike,,0,0,0,,Wait, no! You don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.82,0:14:52.66,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,This changeling replaced your friend to get close to the baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.66,0:14:54.90,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,What other explanation could there be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.90,0:14:56.56,Spike,,0,0,0,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:02.16,Spike,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.08,0:15:06.60,Guard,,0,0,0,,After it! Don't let the changeling escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.60,0:15:08.60,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,I hope your friend is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.90,0:15:13.42,Spike,,0,0,0,,Yeah… me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.65,0:15:24.76,Guard,,0,0,0,,Spike, you should go find Crystalhoof while we hunt down the changeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.76,0:15:27.36,Spike,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure he doesn't wanna see me…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.36,0:15:29.34,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Spread out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.34,0:15:31.95,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,The changeling is probably still nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.85,0:15:39.55,Spike,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'm pretty sure he ran as far away from here as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.55,0:15:43.40,Spike,,0,0,0,,…but I bet I know where!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:46.54,Spike,,0,0,0,,Thorax! Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.54,0:15:48.65,Spike,,0,0,0,,I just want to apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.65,0:15:51.19,Spike,,0,0,0,,I should have stood up for you…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.19,0:15:53.80,Spike,,0,0,0,,Aw, come on, Thorax!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.80,0:15:55.89,Spike,,0,0,0,,I know you're in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:59.35,Thorax,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:04.28,Spike,,0,0,0,,Little help?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.28,0:16:06.57,Thorax,,0,0,0,,Why do you think I would help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.57,0:16:09.21,Thorax,,0,0,0,,I'm an "evil changeling"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.21,0:16:11.61,Spike,,0,0,0,,Because you're my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.61,0:16:13.87,Spike,,0,0,0,,I just wish I had been there for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.71,0:16:23.68,Thorax,,0,0,0,,It's okay, I know it's hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.68,0:16:27.09,Thorax,,0,0,0,,Everyone in the Crystal Empire loves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:30.60,Thorax,,0,0,0,,I couldn't ask you to give that up for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.60,0:16:32.19,Spike,,0,0,0,,You don't have to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.19,0:16:34.08,Thorax,,0,0,0,,What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.08,0:16:37.15,Spike,,0,0,0,,What I should've done in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.52,0:16:50.76,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,I know it's bad that there's a changeling around, but is all this really necessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.76,0:16:54.55,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,If there's one changeling, there may well be a whole army on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.55,0:16:56.89,Twilight,,0,0,0,,True. But Starlight has a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.89,0:16:59.46,Twilight,,0,0,0,,This is getting a little out of hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.46,0:17:02.86,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,I understand, but I don't know what else we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.86,0:17:04.45,Spike,,0,0,0,,I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.18,0:17:07.99,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.99,0:17:08.99,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.99,0:17:10.90,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Get away from that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:13.15,Spike,,0,0,0,,No. He's not a "thing"!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.15,0:17:16.05,Spike,,0,0,0,,His name is Thorax, and he's my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.33,0:17:33.71,Spike,,0,0,0,,Would you say I'm a hero
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.35,0:17:37.04,Spike,,0,0,0,,Glourius and brave
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.24,0:17:40.08,Spike,,0,0,0,,If I told you something
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.26,0:17:42.98,Spike,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't believe
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.59,0:17:47.21,Spike,,0,0,0,,That sometimes I'm scared
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.07,0:17:50.75,Spike,,0,0,0,,And I can make mistakes
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.36,0:17:54.11,Spike,,0,0,0,,And I'm not so heroic
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.69,0:17:57.78,Spike,,0,0,0,,It seems…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.32,0:18:01.30,Spike,,0,0,0,,But if day can turn to night
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.74,0:18:04.74,Spike,,0,0,0,,And the darkness turn to light
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.52,0:18:07.90,Spike,,0,0,0,,Then why can't we imagine
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.07,0:18:11.40,Spike,,0,0,0,,A changeling can change
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.79,0:18:17.33,Spike,,0,0,0,,Not two ponies are exactly the same
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:23.69,Spike,,0,0,0,,No two snowflakes ever match their design
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.68,0:18:28.46,Spike,,0,0,0,,And I thought I was strong
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:32.10,Spike,,0,0,0,,But I was nothing but wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.13,0:18:33.51,Spike,,0,0,0,,When I forgot
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.95,0:18:38.78,Spike,,0,0,0,,To be friendly and kind
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.98,0:18:42.21,Spike,,0,0,0,,But if day can turn to night
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.37,0:18:45.52,Spike,,0,0,0,,And the darkness turn to light
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.93,0:18:48.35,Spike,,0,0,0,,Then why can't we imagine
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.55,0:18:52.20,Spike,,0,0,0,,A changeling can change
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.65,0:18:56.21,Spike,,0,0,0,,Would you say I'm a hero
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.75,0:18:59.37,Spike,,0,0,0,,Glourius and brave
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.85,0:19:02.82,Spike,,0,0,0,,If I told you something
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.82,0:19:05.33,Spike,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't believe
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.29,0:19:10.52,Spike,,0,0,0,,This changeling it seems
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.09,0:19:13.55,Spike,,0,0,0,,Knows the real me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.28,0:19:17.17,Spike,,0,0,0,,And will stay by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.62,0:19:21.23,Spike,,0,0,0,,To the end
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.36,0:19:24.71,Spike,,0,0,0,,So if day can turn to night
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.90,0:19:28.37,Spike,,0,0,0,,And the darkness turn to light
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:31.46,Spike,,0,0,0,,Then why can't we imagine
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.04,0:19:34.76,Spike,,0,0,0,,Just why can't we imagine
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.58,0:19:37.92,Spike,,0,0,0,,Then why can't imagine
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.15,0:19:44.41,Spike,,0,0,0,,The changeling can change
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.35,0:20:00.77,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Spike, I'm so proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.77,0:20:01.59,Spike,,0,0,0,,You are?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.59,0:20:02.81,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.81,0:20:05.07,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You're celebrity here in the Crystal Empire,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.07,0:20:07.59,Twilight,,0,0,0,,and you just risked all of it for a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.59,0:20:10.55,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine anything more brave than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:12.90,Twilight,,0,0,0,,As the Princess of Friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.91,0:20:15.85,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I try to set an example for all of Equestria,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.85,0:20:18.66,Twilight,,0,0,0,,but today it was Spike who taught me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.66,0:20:21.22,Twilight,,0,0,0,,that a new friend can come from anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.22,0:20:25.73,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I guess everypony still has things to learn about friendship, even me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.73,0:20:28.12,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And if Spike says Thorax is his friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:30.12,Twilight,,0,0,0,,then he's my friend too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.96,0:20:33.31,Thorax,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.91,0:20:36.03,Twilight,,0,0,0,,On behalf of the Crystal Empire
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.03,0:20:39.07,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,I would like to extend my hoof in friendship,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.07,0:20:42.92,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,and I'm sure all of my subjects are eager to do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.69,0:20:55.53,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Crystal Empire, Thorax.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.53,0:20:58.34,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry we didnn't take the time to get to know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.34,0:21:00.10,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Maybe we could change that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.74,0:21:02.82,Thorax,,0,0,0,,That would be so amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.82,0:21:05.62,Thorax,,0,0,0,,I wanna know all about friendship and maybe one day,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.62,0:21:08.57,Thorax,,0,0,0,,I can take that knowledge back to the Changeling Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.57,0:21:12.07,Thorax,,0,0,0,,If my kind learn how to create love from one another,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.07,0:21:14.62,Thorax,,0,0,0,,maybe they won't have to take it from others.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.62,0:21:16.91,Somepony,,0,0,0,,To Spike the Brave and Glorious!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.13,0:21:26.99,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Looks like you were right, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.99,0:21:28.21,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Right about what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.21,0:21:31.31,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Friendship lessons can happen anywhere.
